Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.41,0:00:04.65,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A racing second hand, a shooting comet,\Na wind-up doll, and a crowd!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.65,0:00:08.12,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Mystery-solving logic drenches dry hearts and sand walls!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.12,0:00:11.72,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Today's case is about greed and 1 billion yen in gold!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.72,0:00:13.29,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.29,0:00:15.01,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.01,0:00:16.89,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.61,0:01:39.28,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The Ryujin-Maru disappeared 7 years ago
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.28,0:01:44.11,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}with 1 billion yen in gold onboard, but suddenly reappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.95,0:01:46.97,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But the gold was gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.25,0:01:53.02,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The old man was invited to the island,\Nwhich had garnered attention
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.02,0:01:54.55,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}because of the ghost ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.89,0:02:01.13,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}We came here as tourists, but the mayor's true motive
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.13,0:02:05.13,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}was to have the old man locate the missing gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.37,0:02:10.36,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Someone tried to kill him at his lecture.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.98,0:02:14.41,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The culprit was Hamada, the lighthouse keeper with facial burns.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.41,0:02:20.12,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And the suspicious travel agent Uehara seemed to know him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.12,0:02:22.71,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Who exactly are these two?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.35,0:02:26.82,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That night, the old man was attacked by a warrior.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.82,0:02:31.33,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}After narrowly escaping death, he chased his assailant.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.33,0:02:35.79,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Someone knocked him unconscious and framed him
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.27,0:02:40.17,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}as Hamada's killer!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.58,0:02:50.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.58,0:02:54.79,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Mayor of Shikishima\NTakeo Mikami (50)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.58,0:02:52.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if you are a famous detective,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.48,0:02:54.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,you can't get away with murder!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.79,0:02:59.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You got it all wrong! This guy suddenly attacked me in my sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.09,0:03:02.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I chased him here, got hit from behind,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.56,0:03:04.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and when I woke up he was dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.96,0:03:09.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You probably just killed him in a rage!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.03,0:03:10.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.77,0:03:13.98,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Deputy Mayor of Shikishima\NGoro Kinoshita (53)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.37,0:03:15.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But this outfit he's wearing is kept in the {\i1}Suigun{\i0} Artifact Museum...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.71,0:03:18.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why another {\i1}Suigun{\i0} outfit?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.04,0:03:21.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be the curse?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.37,0:03:23.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't be a fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.25,0:03:25.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, it has to be!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.11,0:03:28.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I bet Hamada got possessed and dressed up like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.18,0:03:31.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Be quiet! The curse is just a superstition!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.45,0:03:34.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then why's he dressed like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.16,0:03:35.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, that's—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.26,0:03:39.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, now. There's no point in arguing here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.23,0:03:43.22,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}This sword wound is what killed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.33,0:03:46.83,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Did his sleeve come off during the struggle?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.90,0:03:49.37,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Those are rope marks!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.74,0:03:55.04,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Covered in cuts. But these ones are—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.01,0:03:58.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Children shouldn't look at such things.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.35,0:04:00.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.69,0:04:06.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait! Where are you going, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.03,0:04:12.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}! You'll get in trouble for barging in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.93,0:04:19.03,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}No doubt about it. Hamada{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10} was killed here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.94,0:04:22.37,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It's dry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.37,0:04:23.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that blood?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.67,0:04:25.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}! Get that officer!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.61,0:04:34.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It does look like he was murdered here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.68,0:04:38.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But that doesn't clear the detective's name...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.09,0:04:39.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.46,0:04:43.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The ghosts got mad because an outsider was poking around!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.79,0:04:45.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold on...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.05,0:04:46.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're gonna protect him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.33,0:04:48.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'll be cursed too, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.87,0:04:50.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, you! Stop that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.47,0:04:53.26,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}This doesn't look good...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.71,0:04:58.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.08,0:05:02.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? What's here? The {\i1}Suigun{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.01,0:05:06.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hilarious.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.64,0:05:08.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.15,0:05:11.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know who did it, but if they think they can frame me
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.55,0:05:15.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,with such a childish trick, they're greatly mistaken!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.59,0:05:17.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You mean you didn't do this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.69,0:05:18.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course I didn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.83,0:05:22.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was dead long before I got here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.57,0:05:24.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't give us that crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.17,0:05:27.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The pool of blood on the boat is proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.44,0:05:30.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I killed him, then he only died 30 minutes ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.44,0:05:34.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the blood on the boat is completely dry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.38,0:05:38.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However you look at it, 3 to 4 hours have passed!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.45,0:05:40.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.32,0:05:43.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My attacker was someone other than Hamada.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.72,0:05:46.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That person killed him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.72,0:05:51.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After killing him, they attacked me in {\i1}Suigun{\i0} armor!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.99,0:05:57.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To lure me here and frame me as Hamada's murderer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.57,0:05:58.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.97,0:06:03.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That person tied Hamada up in the boat and tortured him!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.57,0:06:06.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The rope marks on his wrists are proof!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.15,0:06:17.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the cuts all over his body are too numerous and shallow to be fatal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.19,0:06:19.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.12,0:06:23.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words, the killer tied him up and tortured him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.59,0:06:26.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who'd do something so horrible?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.26,0:06:29.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hamada was probably connected to the Ryujin-Maru.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.67,0:06:32.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was probably on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.07,0:06:34.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How do you know about that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.24,0:06:38.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Ryujin-Maru's telescope was on the lighthouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.61,0:06:41.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh? How do you know about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.11,0:06:42.45,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Uh oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.45,0:06:45.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's nothing a great detective doesn't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.11,0:06:48.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, Hamada appeared 7 years ago, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.62,0:06:53.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So it was the gold's location that the killer got from Hamada?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.56,0:06:58.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. Hamada most likely knew where it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.23,0:07:02.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And he moved to the island to guard it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.43,0:07:11.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But he feared I would find it, so he attempted to kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.84,0:07:18.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan and Suzu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} even saw him leave from the backstage door.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.41,0:07:19.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Suzu did?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.78,0:07:25.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But there was yet another person looking for the gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.92,0:07:30.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that person's eyes, Hamada and I were both obstacles.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.39,0:07:33.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That would explain the set up here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.83,0:07:36.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But there's no one here like that—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.53,0:07:39.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's him! That other person from Tokyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.87,0:07:41.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The travel agent?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.32,0:07:43.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was fighting with Hamada!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.97,0:07:45.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.88,0:07:47.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where is he staying?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.23,0:07:49.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The inn, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.88,0:07:52.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's great, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.65,0:07:55.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't do it! Believe me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.31,0:07:57.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, we know you didn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.19,0:08:03.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Officer! Get going!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.95,0:08:07.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've never arrested anyone before!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.63,0:08:09.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez. What're you here for then?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.97,0:08:10.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.90,0:08:12.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's got cold feet!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.74,0:08:14.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I shall go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.79,0:08:16.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Deputy Mayor!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.14,0:08:19.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll try to convince him to turn himself in.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.54,0:08:20.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.58,0:08:23.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was the town hall that asked him here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.58,0:08:26.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's my responsibility as Deputy Mayor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.69,0:08:40.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's been 5 minutes now...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.87,0:08:52.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kinoshita{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.84,0:08:53.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you alright?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.73,0:08:55.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He ran off...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.71,0:08:58.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He escaped out the back! After him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.98,0:09:04.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I tried to persuade him, but he suddenly shot at me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.19,0:09:06.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We need to get you to a doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.72,0:09:10.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll be all right. It's just a scratch.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.19,0:09:16.10,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}No sign of him around the back road. Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.67,0:09:20.69,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}No sign of him here either. Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.34,0:09:25.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good work. Sorry, but could you leave some guards
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.24,0:09:27.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and come back for now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.74,0:09:30.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, now! There's still this area!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.92,0:09:36.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can't ask us to check the {\i1}Suigun{\i0} Cave...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.52,0:09:42.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nobody would dare go near that place. A single officer isn't really—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.36,0:09:44.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What kind of cowardice is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.67,0:09:46.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then why don't you go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.53,0:09:48.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Get serious! Why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.64,0:10:01.61,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}If Uehara killed Hamada{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10},\Nhe must've learned the gold's location.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.61,0:10:06.14,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But if so, then why did he need to search the lighthouse?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.69,0:10:16.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"No Entrance"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.63,0:10:26.90,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Moss?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.90,0:10:30.74,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And this is the kind that grows on land!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.74,0:10:33.74,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I was right; this boat didn't sink!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.74,0:10:39.55,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But would it be possible to hide it\Nfrom the islanders for 7 years?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.55,0:10:40.88,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.62,0:10:50.53,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}There's the {\i1}Suigun{\i0} Cave.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.53,0:10:54.16,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}No one would go near there! What if—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.20,0:11:01.84,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He would've noticed it had he looked through the telescope!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.84,0:11:04.70,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}There was no need to torture Hamada{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.70,0:11:09.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"{\i1}Suigun{\i0} Cave"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.38,0:11:13.44,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Not good. I'll get stopped if I'm seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.25,0:11:17.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's just you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.42,0:11:21.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't you "oh" me! You wanna go to the cave, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.22,0:11:22.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.39,0:11:24.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I happen to know a secret path.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.49,0:11:25.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.93,0:11:28.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where?! Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.40,0:11:31.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How rude! Can't you ask politely?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.40,0:11:34.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.17,0:11:35.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's all?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.14,0:11:36.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What else should I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.78,0:11:42.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You dummy! What're you thinking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.71,0:11:44.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you don't want to, then fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.11,0:11:45.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Darn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.58,0:11:47.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.56,0:11:56.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,OK! I'll show you the way! Follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.03,0:11:58.02,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What a bossy kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.49,0:12:00.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See! Here it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.77,0:12:07.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're not going in, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.41,0:12:08.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.70,0:12:09.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.81,0:12:12.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought you didn't believe in superstitions?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.61,0:12:16.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course I don't! I only asked because I'm concerned about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.71,0:12:19.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can stay here if you're scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.18,0:12:22.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.10,0:12:25.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's just a superstition, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.22,0:12:46.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It looks like Hamada{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} used to look after this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.17,0:12:54.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The ghosts are mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.81,0:13:02.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}! You'll be punished!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.95,0:13:08.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Another cave.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.92,0:13:11.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those weren't ghosts just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.48,0:13:14.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was just a draft resonating inside the cave.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.55,0:13:15.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are we going in?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.47,0:13:16.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.49,0:13:24.93,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}These stairs aren't natural. Someone purposely made them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.07,0:13:29.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's bright up ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.68,0:13:46.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You should make stairs that don't break, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.92,0:13:51.39,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}This moss! This is the place!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.39,0:13:52.12,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Is this—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.12,0:13:53.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.83,0:13:55.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's so pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.24,0:14:06.27,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}There's no moss here. It broke apart recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.27,0:14:09.73,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Ah. The storm opened up the exit and—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.68,0:14:13.05,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Looks like something slid down.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.05,0:14:16.57,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}No doubt about it.\NThe Ryujin-Maru was hidden here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.15,0:14:21.49,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The passageway that the Ryujin-Maru stayed in
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.49,0:14:24.79,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}was demolished by the storm and reopened.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.87,0:14:38.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.15,0:14:52.71,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A suicide?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.02,0:15:00.19,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}No, this was no suicide!\NIn which case, the killer is—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.57,0:15:12.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello? Yes. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.77,0:15:15.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That would really help us out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.74,0:15:17.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. Thanks a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.68,0:15:21.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Detective Mouri! The fishermen are going to lend us a boat
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.91,0:15:24.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,to go by the {\i1}Suigun{\i0} Cave!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.88,0:15:26.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alright! Let's go, Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.49,0:15:29.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, Dad! Have you seen Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.26,0:15:32.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who cares?! He's probably off playing somewhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.93,0:15:34.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.77,0:15:43.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He probably killed himself after accepting that he couldn't escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.87,0:15:45.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kinoshita{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.34,0:15:48.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I followed you when I saw you go inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.44,0:15:50.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, let's go back to town.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.40,0:15:51.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.58,0:15:55.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.05,0:15:58.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This was no suicide. He was murdered.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.62,0:15:59.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can't be serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.67,0:16:01.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look at his wound.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.55,0:16:05.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The hole on the right is bigger than the one on the left.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.99,0:16:09.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This proves the bullet went from left to right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.90,0:16:12.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yet the gun is in his right hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.90,0:16:18.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't it unnatural to shoot from the left with your right hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.77,0:16:25.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that case, there's no longer any need to hide the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.52,0:16:31.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.05,0:16:34.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} doesn't seem surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.29,0:16:37.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You shot yourself in the arm, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.79,0:16:40.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You even realized that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.09,0:16:42.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There were burn marks on the hole in your shirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.76,0:16:46.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which means that you fired with the muzzle pressed against it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.40,0:16:49.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You said that you were suddenly shot at.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.84,0:16:53.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nobody would "suddenly" shoot in such a way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.81,0:16:56.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You impress me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.31,0:16:59.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You also killed Hamada{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.31,0:17:04.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right. I always thought he seemed suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.45,0:17:07.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So I checked the lighthouse while he was gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.82,0:17:09.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I take it you found the telescope?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.99,0:17:16.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. I planned to look for the gold someday at my leisure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.03,0:17:20.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the greedy mayor started needlessly prying...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.17,0:17:26.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Daddy's not greedy! He said you used the town's money!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.91,0:17:33.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I became nervous.\NKogoro Mouri is a peerless detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.95,0:17:39.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was worried he might find the gold first if he started investigating.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.92,0:17:43.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And he got involved, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.82,0:17:49.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you tricked the old man and framed him as Hamada{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.10,0:17:52.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I mistakenly underestimated him, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.43,0:17:56.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you did learn the gold's location from Hamada{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.77,0:18:00.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He finally told me about this place after a bit of pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.01,0:18:04.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just as Mouri said, he had been on the Ryujin-Maru.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.54,0:18:06.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I take it this guy was, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.55,0:18:11.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. Hamada threw him and the owner into the stormy ocean
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.68,0:18:14.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,to keep all the gold for himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.89,0:18:18.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hamada. His real name was apparently Aoki.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.46,0:18:23.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He brought the Ryujin-Maru in here to escape the storm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.13,0:18:28.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the storm tore rocks off and sealed the exit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.40,0:18:33.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He probably didn't plan to,\Nbut there were no other hiding places.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.84,0:18:37.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The islanders stayed away because of the "curse".
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.24,0:18:42.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even more so after he killed the professor to make it look like
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.28,0:18:44.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the {\i1}Suigun{\i0} curse.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.75,0:18:46.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What happened to his face?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.92,0:18:48.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I hear he burned it himself
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.99,0:18:52.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,because he feared someone might recognize him...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.66,0:18:57.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You pretended to get shot by Uehara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} to let him escape, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.60,0:19:01.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he were arrested, Hamada{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s killer and the gold's location
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.27,0:19:02.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,would be found out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.84,0:19:08.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right. He did seem vaguely aware of this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.31,0:19:10.44,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Why are you letting me run?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.44,0:19:15.14,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Never mind that; you're a dead man if they catch you now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.02,0:19:19.89,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I'll hold onto this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.89,0:19:24.92,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Your situation will get even worse\Nif you're caught with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.92,0:19:26.82,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.41,0:19:40.30,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Kinoshita{\rHonorifics - Flashback\be10}-san{\r\be10}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.04,0:19:44.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then you beat him to the cave and killed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.41,0:19:48.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right. Now our discussion is over!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.88,0:19:57.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nobody'll find your bodies here! Ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.96,0:20:00.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.09,0:20:01.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you find the gold?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.96,0:20:05.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's probably buried around here somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.30,0:20:09.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll leisurely look for it after things cool down.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.40,0:20:10.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's so funny?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.97,0:20:14.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'd never find it in 100 years\Nwith your intelligence!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.67,0:20:16.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.44,0:20:17.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You still don't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.92,0:20:19.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You mean you know where?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.75,0:20:21.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. At your feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.02,0:20:26.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.40,0:20:40.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The gold was in these blocks used as part of the stairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.07,0:20:45.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow! I love you, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.87,0:20:47.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.61,0:20:49.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,An earthquake?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.08,0:20:53.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.95,0:20:59.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Take this board to the exit! I'll bring Kinoshita{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.52,0:21:07.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.63,0:21:09.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.97,0:21:15.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.96,0:21:40.13,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}There's probably no way to dig out the gold
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.13,0:21:43.42,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}in the completely-collapsed cave.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.03,0:21:46.90,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I doubt anyone would spend over a billion yen
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.90,0:21:50.70,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}just to dig out a billion yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.70,0:21:56.71,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}In the end, the greed-inducing gold returned to the earth,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.71,0:21:59.20,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}along with the {\i1}Suigun{\i0} curse.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.20,0:23:31.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You idiot! If I hadn't gone to rescue you in the fishing boat,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.57,0:23:33.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,there's no telling what would've happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.01,0:23:41.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you doing to my Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.31,0:23:42.61,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}She's scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.96,0:23:59.43,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It's empty!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.43,0:24:03.87,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I don't get it! Where did the killer disappear to?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.87,0:24:08.74,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Wait! Could it be?! Only he could've done it!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.95,0:24:14.99,Signs,,0,0,0,,Next Conan:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.99,0:24:19.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan's Hint: Paint
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.22,0:24:22.65,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Next time marks the appearance of the giant monster Genta!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.22,0:24:22.65,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10\an8}daikaijū
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.65,0:24:24.86,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Grilled eel lunches!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.65,0:24:24.86,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10\an8}unajū
